description: Nako is a 17-year old cleaning maid and waitress working part-time at Kissuisou. She has a shy and timid personality, with a tendency to avoid unwanted social interaction. She is, however, confident about her swimming ability, having been swimming since she was three, she was nick named the "kappa girl". She, together with Ohana, Minko and Yuina are in the same class at high school.
name: Oshimizu Nako
